---
import Header from "../../components/company/CompanyHeader.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/company/CompanyFooter.astro";

const LAST_UPDATED = "December 7, 2025";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>TRANSPARENCY & LEGAL | PEXA</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@300;400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
      :root {
        --color-bg: #000000;
        --color-text: #FFFFFF;
        --color-muted: #888888;
        --color-border: #222222;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        color: var(--color-text);
        font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }

      /* --- HERO --- */
      .hero {
        padding: 160px 0 60px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      }
      
      .meta-badge {
        font-size: 12px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-weight: 700;
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-size: clamp(50px, 8vw, 90px);
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -4px;
        line-height: 0.9;
        margin: 0 0 20px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .hero p { color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 18px; max-width: 600px; }

      .toc { display: flex; gap: 30px; margin-top: 40px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .toc-link {
        color: var(--color-text);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        transition: opacity 0.3s;
      }
      .toc-link:hover { opacity: 0.5; }

      /* --- CONTENT --- */
      .legal-card {
        padding: 80px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        scroll-margin-top: 100px;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 42px;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
        margin: 0 0 40px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      h3 { 
        font-size: 18px; 
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #FFF; 
        margin: 40px 0 20px; 
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      p, li { 
        font-size: 17px; 
        color: var(--color-muted); 
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      ul { margin: 0 0 30px; padding-left: 20px; }
      li { margin-bottom: 12px; }
      
      a { color: #FFF; text-decoration: underline; }

      /* Accent Box */
      .box {
        padding: 40px;
        background: #0A0A0A;
        border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        margin: 40px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #FFF;
      }
      .box h4 { margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #FFF; }
      .box p { margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #EEE; }

      @media(max-width: 768px) {
        .container { padding: 0 20px; }
        .hero { padding: 120px 0 40px; }
        .section-title { font-size: 32px; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>

    <Header />

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <span class="meta-badge">LAST UPDATED: {LAST_UPDATED}</span>
        <h1>TRANSPARENCY<br/>& LEGAL</h1>
        <p>We believe in absolute transparency regarding our Hybrid Architecture and Usage Limits. No hidden clauses.</p>
        
        <nav class="toc">
          <a class="toc-link" href="#privacy">Privacy Policy</a>
          <a class="toc-link" href="#fair-use">Fair Usage</a>
          <a class="toc-link" href="#terms">Terms of Service</a>
        </nav>
      </section>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <article id="privacy" class="legal-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Privacy Policy</h2>
          
          <div class="box">
            <h4>THE HYBRID SECURE ARCHITECTURE</h4>
            <p>PEXA uses a split-data approach to ensure maximum privacy. Your conversations stay with Apple, while your account limits are managed by our secure cloud.</p>
          </div>

          <h3>1. Chat History (Stored in iCloud)</h3>
          <p>Your text prompts, chat history, and generated image references are stored in your personal <strong>iCloud Private Storage</strong>. This data is encrypted by Apple. We (Ashak Studios) strictly do not have access to read your conversations or see your generated images.</p>

          <h3>2. Account Data (Stored in Secure Cloud)</h3>
          <p>To manage your credits, subscription status, and usage limits, we use an industry-standard Secure Cloud Database. When you use "Sign in with Apple", <strong>we strictly do not store your email address</strong> or personal details. We only store:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Your unique User ID provided by Apple (to identify your account).</li>
            <li>Your Pexa credit balance and daily usage counters.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>3. Device Identification</h3>
          <p>To prevent abuse of our free tier and protect the service integrity, we may store a securely <strong>hashed device identifier</strong>. This identifier is anonymized, not linked to your personal chat content, and is used solely to enforce usage policies.</p>

          <h3>4. Right to Erasure (Delete Account)</h3>
          <p>You have full control. If you choose <strong>"Delete Account"</strong> within the app:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Cloud Account:</strong> Your user record and credit data are permanently wiped from our secure servers.</li>
            <li><strong>iCloud:</strong> The app automatically instructs iCloud to wipe your chat history container associated with PEXA.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article id="fair-use" class="legal-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Fair Usage & Limits Policy</h2>
          <p>PEXA relies on high-performance GPU computing power. To ensure the system remains fast and stable for all users, we enforce dynamic limits based on usage intensity.</p>

          <h3>Free Tier</h3>
          <p>Free users operate on a <strong>Credit System</strong>. Once your initial credits are depleted, you may continue generating images by supporting the app (e.g., watching ads).</p>

          <h3>Premium Smart Limits</h3>
          <p>While Premium offers "Unlimited" access to the generation engine, "Unlimited" is defined by <strong>reasonable human use</strong>. To prevent bot abuse and server overheating, the following automated cool-down logic applies to high-frequency users:</p>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>At 20 Rapid Generations:</strong> A short cool-down of <strong>10 minutes</strong> applies ("System Hot").</li>
            <li><strong>At 40 Rapid Generations:</strong> A cool-down of <strong>20 minutes</strong> applies ("Cooling Down").</li>
            <li><strong>At 60 Daily Generations:</strong> To ensure fair resource allocation, a <strong>12-hour reset period</strong> may apply if this limit is hit within a short timeframe.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <article id="terms" class="legal-card">
          <h2 class="section-title">Terms of Service</h2>
          
          <h3>1. Content Safety</h3>
          <p>All text prompts are analyzed by our <strong>automated AI safety system</strong> before image generation. You agree not to attempt to generate content involving Child Sexual Abuse Material (CSAM), gore, extreme violence, or hate speech.</p>

          <h3>2. Authentication</h3>
          <p>PEXA uses <strong>Sign in with Apple</strong> for secure authentication. You are responsible for maintaining the security of your Apple ID. We are not liable for data loss resulting from a compromised Apple account.</p>

          <h3>3. Ownership</h3>
          <p><strong>You own the images you create.</strong> Ashak Studios claims no copyright over your creations. You are free to use them for personal or commercial purposes, subject to local laws regarding AI-generated content.</p>

          <h3>4. Subscriptions & Refunds</h3>
          <p>PEXA offers renewable subscriptions processed entirely by Apple (StoreKit 2).</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Payment is charged to your Apple ID.</li>
            <li>Subscriptions auto-renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the period in your iPhone Settings.</li>
            <li><strong>Refunds:</strong> As developers, we do not have access to your billing information. All refund requests must be handled directly by Apple Support.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>5. Contact</h3>
          <p>For support or inquiries: <a href="mailto:contact@ashak.co">contact@ashak.co</a></p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>